OL,3,CPrimary school set to close
OL,5,FA primary school in Dumfries and
OL,6,FGalloway is set to close at the end of
OL,7,Fthe current academic year.
OL,9,FKirkbean Primary currently has just 10
OL,10,Fpupils enrolled in the school.
OL,12,FIt will be "mothballed" at the end of
OL,13,Fterm four after another low intake of
OL,14,Fstudents was predicted for next year.
OL,16,FIn a statement on social media, the
OL,17,FHeadteacher said parents made the
OL,18,Fdecision to give the community
OL,19,F"dignity", adding that at this
OL,20,Fdecision had "not been taken lightly".
