OL,3,CPrimary school set to close
OL,5,FA spokesperson from Dumfries and
OL,6,FGalloway Council said: "Due to the
OL,7,Fvery low numbers at the school, the
OL,8,Fparents of Kirkbean Primary School
OL,9,Fhave made the decision to move their
OL,10,Fchildren to alternative schools at the
OL,11,Fend of the current academic session.
OL,13,F"Officers will work with the parents
OL,14,Fthrough this transition phase and a
OL,15,Fpaper will be brought to the council's
OL,16,FEducation & Learning Committee in due
OL,17,Fcourse to advise them of this and to
OL,18,Fagree next steps for the school."
